Key Match Events: DL Hall worked 7 scoreless innings in the best start of his career
Willy Adames and Rhys Hoskins each homered and drove in three runs
The Brewers scored 10 runs in the ninth inning to pound the Reds 14-0
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the fourth game in the regular season series between the Brewers and Reds
Others: The game was played at Great American Ball Park in Cincinnati, Ohio, with an attendance of 22,488
